#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This module allows you to configure your pointing device. Your pointing "
#| "device may be a mouse, a track ball, a touch-pad, or another piece of "
#| "hardware that performs a similar function."
msgid ""
"This module allows you to configure your pointing device. Your pointing "
"device may be a mouse, a trackball, a touchpad, or another piece of hardware "
"that performs a similar function."
msgstr ""
"이 모듈에서는 포인팅 장치를 설정할 수 있습니다. 마우스, 트랙볼, 터치패드 및 "
"기타 포인팅 장치를 포함합니다."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:38
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "일반"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:42
#, no-c-format
msgid "Left handed mouse"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:43
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you are left-handed, you may prefer to swap the functions of the "
#| "<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> and <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> "
#| "buttons on your pointing device by choosing the <guilabel>Left handed</"
#| "guilabel> option. If your pointing device has more than two buttons, only "
#| "those that function as the <mousebutton>left</mousebutton> and "
#| "<mousebutton>right</mousebutton> buttons are affected. For example, if "
#| "you have a three-button mouse, the <mousebutton>middle</mousebutton> "
#| "button is unaffected."
msgid ""
"If you are left-handed, you may prefer to swap the functions of the "
"<mousebutton>left</mousebutton> and <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> buttons "
"on your pointing device by checking this option. If your pointing device has "
"more than two buttons, only those that function as the <mousebutton>left</"
"mousebutton> and <mousebutton>right</mousebutton> buttons are affected. For "
"example, if you have a three-button mouse, the <mousebutton>middle</"
"mousebutton> button is unaffected."
msgstr ""
"만약 왼손잡이면 <guilabel>'왼손잡이'</guilabel> 설정을 사용하여 마우스와 같"
"은 포인팅 장치의 <mousebutton>왼쪽</mousebutton> 단추와 <mousebutton>오른쪽</"
"mousebutton> 단추를 바꿀 수 있습니다. 만약 포인팅 장치에 두 개 이상의 단추가 "
"있다면 <mousebutton>왼쪽</mousebutton>과 <mousebutton>오른쪽</mousebutton> 단"
"추만 바뀝니다. 예를 들어 3개 단추 마우스를 이용한다면 <mousebutton>가운데</"
"mousebutton> 단추는 이 기능이 적용되지 않습니다."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "Press left and right buttons for middle-click"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Check this item if you don't have a &MMB;. You can press the left and right "
"mouse buttons at the same time to emulate middle-click."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:66
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Pointer threshold"
msgid "Pointer speed"
msgstr "포인터 최소 이동 거리"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:67
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "This option allows you to change the relationship between the distance "
#| "that the mouse pointer moves on the screen and the relative movement of "
#| "the physical device itself (which may be a mouse, track-ball, or some "
#| "other pointing device.)"
msgid ""
"This option allows you to change the relationship between the distance that "
"the mouse pointer moves on the screen and the relative movement of the "
"physical device itself (which may be a mouse, trackball, or some other "
"pointing device.)"
msgstr ""
"이 옵션을 사용하면 물리적인 장치(마우스, 트랙볼 등)의 상대적인 움직임과 화면"
"에서 마우스 포인터가 이동한 거리의 상관 관계를 설정할 수 있습니다."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Pointer acceleration"
msgstr "포인터 가속"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Standard</guilabel> mode adjusts the amount of pointer "
"acceleration according to how fast you move the mouse. If you set it to "
"<guilabel>None</guilabel>, the acceleration remains constant regardless of "
"speed."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:85
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Reverse scroll direction"
msgid "Scrolling: Invert scroll direction"
msgstr "스크롤 방향 뒤집기"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "With this check box selected, the scroll wheel (if any) will work in the "
#| "opposite direction (so that if rolling the top of the scroll wheel "
#| "towards you previously causes a scroll down, then it will now cause a "
#| "scroll up). This may be useful to handle a unusual setup of the X server."
msgid ""
"With this check box selected, the scroll wheel (if any) will work in the "
"opposite direction (so that if rolling the top of the scroll wheel towards "
"you previously causes a scroll down, then it will now cause a scroll up)."
msgstr ""
"이 상자를 선택하면 스크롤 휠 및 동작의 방향을 반대로 뒤집습니다. 예를 들어서 "
"스크롤 휠을 위에서 아래로 굴릴 때 화면 내용을 아래로 스크롤하는 대신 위로 스"
"크롤하게 됩니다. 특수한 X 서버 설정을 사용할 때 필요할 수 있습니다."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In &plasma; 5.13 you find the setting to use single or double mouse clicks "
"to open files and folders in the module <ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/"
"workspaceoptions/index.html\">Workspace</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"&plasma; 5.13에서는 파일과 폴더를 열 때 마우스 단추를 눌러야 하는 횟수를 "
"<ulink url=\"help:/kcontrol/workspaceoptions/index.html\">작업 공간</ulink> "
"모듈에서 설정할 수 있습니다."

